==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Felting
<hw>Felt"ing</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>The material of which
felt is made; also, felted cloth; also, the process by which it is
made.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>The act of splitting timber by the felt
grain.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Feltry</ent>⟦br⟧
